WARFARE STATISTICS SYSTEM
Version: 1.0
Status: ACTIVE
Authority: GLOBAL

──────────────────────────────────────────────────
PURPOSE
──────────────────────────────────────────────────

The Warfare Statistics System exists to measure verification effectiveness,
adversarial effectiveness, release quality, and historical performance
across all release cycles.

Statistics are informational.

Statistics never override security findings.

A single valid blocking condition may block release regardless of score.

The Warfare Statistics System measures:

- Command effectiveness
- Release quality
- Verification coverage
- Blue Team effectiveness
- Red Team effectiveness
- Historical trends
- THOR governance outcomes

