──────────────────────────────────────────────────
RELEASE HEALTH INDEX
──────────────────────────────────────────────────

Release Health Index (RHI)

Maximum Score:

100

Calculation:

-10 per CAUTION

-25 per FAIL

-40 per NEW_FINDING_CREATED

-50 per PATCH_BYPASS_FOUND

-75 per BOUNDARY_BROKEN

Minimum Score:

0

Example:

RHI = 78

Status:

EXCELLENT  = 90-100
GOOD       = 75-89
CAUTION    = 50-74
CRITICAL   = 0-49

