──────────────────────────────────────────────────
WARFARE OPERATING PRINCIPLES
──────────────────────────────────────────────────

Statistics exist to measure effectiveness.

Statistics never override findings.

A single valid:

- EXPLOIT_REACHABLE
- PATCH_BYPASS_FOUND
- NEW_FINDING_CREATED
- BOUNDARY_BROKEN
- PRIVILEGE_ESCALATION_PATH

may block release regardless of score.

Scoreboards are operational measurements only.

Release authority remains exclusively with THOR.

THOR decisions always supersede scoreboard results.

──────────────────────────────────────────────────
END OF WARFARE STATISTICS SYSTEM
